Package: spatialData
Title: Spatial Datasets for Ecological Modeling
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Blas M.", "Benito", , "blasbenito@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides nine spatial datasets for ecological and environmental
    modelling, covering species distribution modelling, biodiversity analysis,
    and climate-change projections. Datasets include Neanderthal presence records
    with Last Interglacial paleoclimate predictors; global NDVI records with
    environmental predictors; European oak species occurrences; plant diversity
    metrics for global ecoregions; tree species richness across the Americas;
    plant community records from the Sierra Nevada (Spain) with future climate
    scenarios; butterfly-plant interaction data from the Sierra Nevada; threatened
    plant species occurrences in Andalusia; and presence records of the endemic
    plant Linaria nigricans with greenhouse land-use data. All datasets include
    pre-processed environmental predictors ready for statistical modelling.
URL: https://blasbenito.github.io/spatialData, https://github.com/BlasBenito/spatialData
